    ],
    groups: ['Infantry', 'Ranged', 'Cavalry', 'HorseArcher'],
    notes: 'Rohan has one of the strongest cavalry forces in the game. Their infantry and archers are weaker by comparison — meant to hold the line while the cavalry delivers the decisive blow, not to lead charges on their own.',
